FundsAvailableResult.description: Result of a funds availability check.

FundsAvailableDateTime.description:
Date and time at which the funds availability check was generated.All dates in the JSON payloads are represented in ISO 8601 date-time format. 
All date-time fields in responses must include the timezone. An example is below:
2020-04-05T10:43:07+03:00

FundsAvailable.description: Flag to indicate the availability of funds given the Amount in the consent request.
